    "title": "Front Office Manager - Taj Hotels - Top MNC",
    "description": "Grow your career with Taj Hotels! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Ludhiana team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Taj Hotels:\nTaj Hotels is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Taj Hotels!",
